CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Globavend Holdings Ltd is an Australia-based company, which is engaged in offering direct injections focusing on Australia and New Zealand. The Company delivers e-commerce parcels to Australian and New Zealand consumers. Customers generate labels using the Company's systems and they deliver parcels to the Company's facilities, then the Company delivers tracked parcels to the customers in Australia and New Zealand.
